---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="article-grid-section">
    <h2 class="grid-heading">About</h2>
  </section>

  <div class="about-layout">
    <div class="about-body">
      <h1 class="about-heading">We write about AI and automation for the people building with it.</h1>
      <p>The Knowledge Hub is a publication by <strong>Semantic Technology Services</strong> — a Canadian technology consultancy helping enterprises design, deploy, and govern AI systems.</p>
      <p>We started this publication because most AI coverage falls into one of two traps: breathless hype or reflexive scepticism. Neither is useful if you're actually trying to decide whether to automate your back office, evaluate a new LLM vendor, or explain a compliance risk to your board.</p>
      <p>Our writers are practitioners — people who have shipped real systems, made real mistakes, and learned what the benchmarks don't tell you. Every piece we publish is written to be useful to someone making a real decision.</p>

      <h2 class="about-subheading">What we cover</h2>
      <ul class="about-list">
        <li><strong>Automation</strong> — workflow design, RPA, document processing, and the operational realities of removing humans from repetitive work.</li>
        <li><strong>AI in the enterprise</strong> — LLMs, RAG pipelines, fine-tuning, and how to think about build vs. buy.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics</strong> — data infrastructure, BI tooling, and how to turn raw data into decisions.</li>
        <li><strong>Policy & governance</strong> — Canadian AI regulation, data privacy, and what compliance actually requires of your systems.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="about-subheading">Who we are</h2>
      <p>Semantic Technology Services is based in Canada. We work with mid-market and enterprise clients across financial services, healthcare, logistics, and the public sector. If you're interested in working with us, <a href="/contact">get in touch</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <aside class="about-aside">
      <div class="about-aside-block">
        <p class="aside-label">Publisher</p>
        <p>Semantic Technology Services</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-aside-block">
        <p class="aside-label">Based in</p>
        <p>Canada</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-aside-block">
        <p class="aside-label">Focus areas</p>
        <p>AI, Automation, Analytics, Governance</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-aside-block">
        <p class="aside-label">Contact</p>
        <a href="/contact">Send us a message →</a>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .about-heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-body p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-body p strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about-body a {
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .about-subheading {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-list li {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-list li strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about-aside {
    position: sticky;
    top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .about-aside-block {
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .aside-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .about-aside-block p:last-child,
  .about-aside-block a {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .about-aside-block a {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-aside {
      position: static;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      border-top: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      gap: 0;
    }

    .about-aside-block {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: none;
    }
  }
</style>
